          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best school in Gurgaon.The faculty are dedicated and truly care about the students’ growth, both academically and personally. There is a strong focus on fostering creativity, critical thinking, and collaboration among students. The school also offers a wide range of extracurricular activities, providing students with opportunities to explore their interests beyond the classroom. The campus is well-maintained, and the resources available to students are top-notch. Overall, this school creates a nurturing environment that encourages learning, personal development, and a sense of community. Highly recommend it!",
